snippet.title: PowerWash Simulator - How Far We've Come! (Stream VOD)
snippet.description:
Watch our PowerWash Simulator Developer Livestream showcasing new features and some funny moments making dirt art! What is PowerWash Simulator you may ask? Well - it is a game where you a budding power washing business must clean dirt off clients vehicles, buildings and even giant shoes! Grow your business and take on larger and wackier jobs, plus, unlock new power washers, nozzles, soaps equipment and more!

Like power washing? This is the game for you! Wishlist this satisfying simulator ahead of Steam Early Access here: https://bit.ly/WishlistPWS

Keep up with all our socials on Twitter: https://bit.ly/TwitterPWS
and TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@powerwashsim

#powerwashsimulator #gaming #powerwashing #satisfying

Let the soothing sounds of high-pressure water wash away your worries. Fire up your powerwasher and blast away every speck of dirt and grime you can find. Release the Pressure, with PowerWash Simulator.

Subscribe to this channel for more gameplay and development insights from us, FuturLab!
